headline: Keith Urban Announces the Winner of Old El Paso’s "Castin’ the Cowboy" Content Series
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, July 14, 2025--After weeks of taco ballads, big belt buckles and taco-fueled performances, Old El Paso’s wildly flavorful "Castin’ the Cowboy" content series has officially come to a close, with Keith Urban crowning a new taco night icon: Elroy, a larger-than-life cowboy with the chops to match his charm.
